creator: Super Speed.
descriptionHtml:
iClean is one of the most effective Super Junk Clean Masters for Android phone and boost your devices for better performance. With the master cleaner - iClean, users can clean junk files, clean cache files, scan & clean viruses, boost memory or boost space, cool down your phone, lock apps for privacy or even save more battery.

💖Enjoy a more easier cleaning experience with New feature Auto Clean! Just set your own time interval in iClean and make it running background, it will automatically remove the junk files on your device.

^ iCLEAN FEATURES ^
✔️ Clean cache and junk files to gain additional space
✔️ Free up storage & boost memory to make phone super faster than ever
✔️ Clean & boost your SNS apps like WhatsApp or Line
✔️ Set notification reminders for quicker phone optimization
✔️ Scan and clean potential virus to make your device safe
✔️ Lock and unlock every privacy file & app easily with one tap
✔️ Navigate and stop overheating apps
✔️ Find battery-draining apps and save battery effectively

^ FEATURES & CAPABILITIES ^
💥 Super Junk Cleaner
If your phone is not up to speed and gets hang, just use iClean to remove junks or cache and gain additional storage space. iClean will help to analyze and clean junk files, system cache, residual files, useless APKs, ads junk and temporary files. Clean cache and boost your Android device with super easily one tap now!

🚀 Super Phone Booster
iClean can scan and navigate the apps which occupied too much memory space. Equipped with a super intelligent analytical mechanism, iClean will detect and terminate all the processes that occupying a huge part of the storage space hence boosting memory for better performance.

🔰 Virus Cleaner
If iClean detects malware, spyware, rootkits, hackers or online fraud, it will act as a virus cleaner which will block viruses, dangerous apps, dangerous APKs, links, or files. iClean will always give you real-time protection! With powerful & FREE virus cleaner, iClean will protect your device from any virus threats while you’re using your device.

🔒 App Lock
App Lock will protect your private information safe & secure by adding an extra fingerprint, pattern or passcode for apps like Facebook, Messenger, WhatsApp, Gallery or anything you want. Using App Lock, you can lock or unlock your sensitive apps easily with one tap.

🥇 WhatsApp & Line Cleaner
There is a specified clean function only for WhatsApp and Line. With this powerful function, iClean will help to scan and clean all the residual files including useless videos, photos, and audios of your SNS apps but will never clean your chat logs.

🤖Personalized Notification
Sometimes you may get so busy to check whether your phone got any abnormal behavior which may lead to a slow and lagging phone. iClean can remind you whenever your phone gets low storage space, low battery, too much cache or high CPU temperature, hence optimize the phone as quickly as possible. Activate the feature and enjoy a convenient phone optimizing service.

🌡️ CPU Cooler
iClean will dynamically analyze and optimize your CPU usage. Find and stop overheating apps to cool down phone temperature. With iClean’s CPU Cooler Master, your CPU temperature will be cooled down fast! Also, it will prevent your phone temperature from rising again.

🔋 Battery Saver
When battery-draining apps found, iClean will act as a battery doctor to cut down unnecessary processes and save more battery for your phone.

If you like iClean, please rate us 5 stars! ★ ★ ★ ★ ★

📌iClean Notes
1. iClean will keep your information secure and will never share it with the third party according to the Privacy and Cookies Policy.
2. Fingerprint lock works only with devices running Android 6.0 or higher and fingerprint sensor support.

Feel free to send us your thoughts on iClean at iclean@topappstudio.com for further assistance!

💥 Super Junk Cleaner

🚀 Super Phone Booster

With the master cleaner - iClean, users can clean junk files, clean cache files, scan & clean viruses, boost memory or boost space, cool down your phone, lock apps for privacy or even save more battery.

💖Enjoy a more easier cleaning experience with New feature Auto Clean! Just set your own time interval in iClean and make it running background, it will automatically remove the junk files on your device.

^ iCLEAN FEATURES ^
✔️ Clean cache and junk files to gain additional space
✔️ Free up storage & boost memory to make phone super faster than ever
✔️ Clean & boost your SNS apps like WhatsApp or Line
✔️ Set notification reminders for quicker phone optimization
✔️ Scan and clean potential virus to make your device safe
✔️ Lock and unlock every privacy file & app easily with one tap
✔️ Navigate and stop overheating apps
✔️ Find battery-draining apps and save battery effectively

^ FEATURES & CAPABILITIES ^
💥 Super Junk Cleaner
If your phone is not up to speed and gets hang, just use iClean to remove junks or cache and gain additional storage space. iClean will help to analyze and clean junk files, system cache, residual files, useless APKs, ads junk and temporary files. Clean cache and boost your Android device with super easily one tap now!

🚀 Super Phone Booster
iClean can scan and navigate the apps which occupied too much memory space. Equipped with a super intelligent analytical mechanism, iClean will detect and terminate all the processes that occupying a huge part of the storage space hence boosting memory for better performance.

🔰 Virus Cleaner
If iClean detects malware, spyware, rootkits, hackers or online fraud, it will act as a virus cleaner which will block viruses, dangerous apps, dangerous APKs, links, or files. iClean will always give you real-time protection! With powerful & FREE virus cleaner, iClean will protect your device from any virus threats while you’re using your device.

🔒 App Lock
App Lock will protect your private information safe & secure by adding an extra fingerprint, pattern or passcode for apps like Facebook, Messenger, WhatsApp, Gallery or anything you want. Using App Lock, you can lock or unlock your sensitive apps easily with one tap.

🥇 WhatsApp & Line Cleaner
There is a specified clean function only for WhatsApp and Line. With this powerful function, iClean will help to scan and clean all the residual files including useless videos, photos, and audios of your SNS apps but will never clean your chat logs.

🤖Personalized Notification
Sometimes you may get so busy to check whether your phone got any abnormal behavior which may lead to a slow and lagging phone. iClean can remind you whenever your phone gets low storage space, low battery, too much cache or high CPU temperature, hence optimize the phone as quickly as possible. Activate the feature and enjoy a convenient phone optimizing service.

🌡️ CPU Cooler
iClean will dynamically analyze and optimize your CPU usage. Find and stop overheating apps to cool down phone temperature. With iClean’s CPU Cooler Master, your CPU temperature will be cooled down fast! Also, it will prevent your phone temperature from rising again.

🔋 Battery Saver
When battery-draining apps found, iClean will act as a battery doctor to cut down unnecessary processes and save more battery for your phone.

If you like iClean, please rate us 5 stars! ★ ★ ★ ★ ★

📌iClean Notes
1. iClean will keep your information secure and will never share it with the third party according to the Privacy and Cookies Policy.
2. Fingerprint lock works only with devices running Android 6.0 or higher and fingerprint sensor support.

Feel free to send us your thoughts on iClean at iclean@topappstudio.com for further assistance!

creator: Super Speed.
descriptionHtml:
Nova Cleaner is an effective Junk Cleaner for Android phones and boosts your devices for better performance. With the super clean helper - Nova Cleaner, users can clean junk files, clean cache files, scan & clean viruses, boost memory or boost space, cool down your phone, lock apps for privacy or even save more battery. Keep your phone super clean by all means!

💖Enjoy an easier cleaning experience with the New feature Auto Clean! Just set your time interval in Nova Cleaner and make it running background, it will automatically remove the junk files on your device.

^ Nova Cleaner FEATURES ^
✔️ Super clean cache and junk files to gain more space
✔️ Free up storage & boost memory to make the phone super faster than ever
✔️ Clean & boost your SNS apps like WhatsApp or Line
✔️ Set notification reminders for quicker phone optimization
✔️ Scan and clean potential viruses to make your device safe
✔️ Lock and unlock every privacy file & app easily with one tap
✔️ Navigate and stop overheating apps
✔️ Find battery-draining apps and save battery effectively

^ FEATURES & CAPABILITIES ^
💥 Super Junk Cleaner
If your phone is not up to speed and gets hung, just use Nova Cleaner to remove junk & cache and gain additional storage. Nova Cleaner will help to analyze and clean junk files, system cache, residual files, useless APKs, ads junk, and temporary files. Super clean cache and boost your Android device with a super-easy one-tap now!

🚀 Super Phone Booster
Nova Cleaner can scan and navigate the apps which occupied too much memory space. Equipped with a super-intelligent analytical mechanism, Nova Cleaner will detect and terminate all the processes occupying a huge part of the storage space, boosting memory for better performance.

🔰 Virus Cleaner
If Nova Cleaner detects a malware, spyware, rootkits, hackers, or online fraud, it will act as a virus cleaner that will block viruses, dangerous apps, dangerous APKs, links, or files. Nova Cleaner will always give you real-time protection! With a powerful & FREE virus cleaner, Nova Cleaner will protect your device from any virus threats while you’re using your device.

🔒 App Lock
App Lock will protect your private information safe & secure by adding an extra fingerprint, pattern, or passcode for apps like Facebook, Messenger, WhatsApp, Gallery, or anything you want. Using App Lock, you can easily lock or unlock your sensitive apps with one tap.

🥇 WhatsApp & Line Cleaner
There is a specified super clean feature only for WhatsApp and Line. With this powerful feature, Nova Cleaner will help to scan and clean all the residual files including useless videos, photos, and audios of your SNS apps but will never clean your chat logs.

🤖Personalized Notification
Sometimes you may get so busy checking whether your phone got any abnormal behavior which may lead to a slow and lagging phone. Nova Cleaner can remind you whenever your phone gets low storage space, low battery, too much cache, or high CPU temperature, hence optimizing the phone as quickly as possible. Activate the feature and enjoy a super clean phone.

🌡️ CPU Cooler
Nova Cleaner will dynamically analyze and optimize your CPU usage. Find and stop overheating apps to cool down phone temperature. With Nova Cleaner’s CPU Cooler Master, your CPU temperature will be cooled down fast!

📌Nova Cleaner Notes
1. Nova Cleaner will keep your information secure and will never share it with a third party according to the Privacy and Cookies Policy.
2. Fingerprint lock works only with Android 6.0 or higher devices and fingerprint sensor support.
3. Accessibility Service: We request Accessibility to provide a deep clean service and we promise that the permission will not be used in reading any of your privacy information or changing your settings.

If you like Nova Cleaner, please rate us 5 stars! ★ ★ ★ ★ ★
Email：novacleaner@topappstudio.com

descriptionHtml:
Nova Cleaner is an effective Junk Cleaner for Android phones and boosts your devices for better performance. With the super clean helper - Nova Cleaner, users can clean junk files, clean cache files, scan & clean viruses, boost memory or boost space, cool down their phone, lock apps for privacy, or even save more battery. Keep your phone super clean by all means!

💖Enjoy an easier cleaning experience with the New feature Auto Clean! Just set your time interval in Nova Cleaner and make it running background, it will automatically remove the junk files on your device.

^ Nova Cleaner FEATURES ^
✔️ Super clean cache and junk files to gain more space
✔️ Free up storage & boost memory to make the phone super faster than ever
✔️ Clean & boost your SNS apps like WhatsApp or Line
✔️ Set notification reminders for quicker phone optimization
✔️ Scan and clean potential viruses to make your device safe
✔️ Lock and unlock every privacy file & app easily with one tap
✔️ Navigate and stop overheating apps
✔️ Find battery-draining apps and save battery effectively

^ FEATURES & CAPABILITIES ^
💥 Super Junk Cleaner
If your phone is not up to speed and gets hung, just use Nova Cleaner to remove junk & cache and gain additional storage. Nova Cleaner will help to analyze and clean junk files, system cache, residual files, useless APKs, ads junk, and temporary files. Super clean cache and boost your Android device with a super-easy one-tap now!

🚀 Super Phone Booster
Nova Cleaner can scan and navigate apps that occupy too much memory space. Equipped with a super-intelligent analytical mechanism, Nova Cleaner will detect and terminate all the processes occupying a huge part of the storage space, boosting memory for better performance.

🔰 Virus Cleaner
If Nova Cleaner detects malware, spyware, rootkits, hackers, or online fraud, it will act as a virus cleaner that will block viruses, dangerous apps, dangerous APKs, links, or files. Nova Cleaner will always give you real-time protection! With a powerful & FREE virus cleaner, Nova Cleaner will protect your device from any virus threats while you’re using your device.

🔒 App Lock
App Lock will protect your private information safe & secure by adding an extra fingerprint, pattern, or passcode for apps like Facebook, Messenger, WhatsApp, Gallery, or anything you want. You can easily lock your sensitive apps with App Lock.

🥇 WhatsApp & Line Cleaner
There is a specified super clean feature only for WhatsApp and Line. Nova Cleaner will help to scan and clean all the residual files including useless videos, photos, and audio of your SNS apps but will never clean your chat logs.

🤖Personalized Notification
Nova Cleaner can remind you whenever your phone gets low storage space, low battery, too much cache, or high CPU temperature, hence optimizing the phone as quickly as possible. Activate the feature and enjoy a super clean phone.

🌡️ CPU Cooler
Nova Cleaner will dynamically analyze and optimize your CPU usage. Find and stop overheating apps to cool down phone temperature. With Nova Cleaner’s CPU Cooler Master, your CPU temperature will be cooled down fast!

📌Nova Cleaner Notes
1. Nova Cleaner will keep your information secure and will never share it with a third party according to the Privacy and Cookies Policy.
2. Fingerprint lock works only with Android 6.0 or higher devices and fingerprint sensor support.
3. Accessibility Service: We request Accessibility to provide a deep clean service and promise that the permission will not be used to read any of your private information or change your settings.
4. VPN service: This app provides a VPN connection service for Android 5.0 and above users for remote access, and guarantees that it will not read any of your personal privacy information or change your settings.
